CSS-7 Basic of CSS Selector

<style>
  a {

  }
  .saw{

  }
  #active {

  }
</style>

powerful selector ; id > class > tag

why? id must be use once, tag selector cover with many stuff than id, class selector


  CSS- 8 Box Model

h1 tag --> block level element

a tag --> inline element

 --> There are some tag for block or inline element But you can also switch whatever you want
 for example even if h1 tag is fix for block element, you can change it in inline element.

caniuse.com - fuction of css html css, ex) Is it work on IE, Opera, Chrome ect...??


  CSS - 10 Grid - layout

<style>
  #grid{
    border:5px solid pink;
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns: 150px(*first) 1fr(*rest of them);
  }

  div{
    border:5px solid gray;
  }
</style>

<body>
  <div id="grid"> *value - you can decide whatever you want)
    <div>NAVIGATION</div>
    <div>ARTICLE</div>
  </div>
</body>


  CSS - 12 Media Query ; Responsive Web (when you make narrow of web then all the letter or
  picture also make in proper size following pixel)
<style>
  div{
    border;10px; solid green;
    font-size:60px;
  }

  @media(min-width:800px)
    div{
      display:none;   *Do not show on display
    }
</style>
<body>
  <div>
    Responsive
  </div>
</body>

